citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:30 pm on 01-
DEC-23.
USDA arrived on property and called the two numbers provided by the licensee. The licensee answered the phone and
stated she was not instate and could not be available for inspection today. USDA reminded the licensee that this was one
of the days listed on her optimal hours and this would be cited as an attempted inspection.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:30 pm on 01-
DEC-23. 
 
USDA arrived on property and called the two numbers provided by the licensee. The licensee answered the phone and 
stated she was not instate and could not be available for inspection today. USDA reminded the licensee that this was one 
of the days listed on her optimal hours and this would be cited as an attempted inspection. 
 
 
End Section
